{"tid":656044,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(連登仔越鬧越紅) 袁澧林獲徐克青睞","createTime":"2018-05-07T01:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T02:28:33.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"442d2f90fadaeb13610048b00b6b326518c8f933","tid":656044,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:49:17.000Z","msg":"繼陳偉霆後, 又一越鬧越紅既例子? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180425/20371751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20371751&d=0MpMz%2FslAsbCWiS2CmIrqJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d7583934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20371751&h=e27a6a50\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180425/20371751</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月25日 <br />\n袁澧林獲徐克青睞<br />\n<br />\n現年24歲的「文青女神」袁澧林（Angela）去年浸會大學會計系畢業後，全力投入娛樂圈發展。之前拍過ViuTV的《三一如三》，電影演出過《那一年，我17》及聲演《超級無敵世界波》。近日她頻頻北上，本月初她穿梭北京、杭州兩地試鏡。她已經落實擔演一套內地電視劇，亦是她首部古裝演出。這兩天會在橫店開工，同劇還有宣萱。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Angela憑脫俗外形，獲導演徐克青睞，有意找她在新作《神鵰俠侶》演出。據知，屬意她飾演原著中不食人間煙火的小龍女，但仍要待這兩天Angela在北京跟徐克見面後，才有最後定奪。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：李森"},{"pid":"7c384b6a2983efa799bb443f73a6de12ec5a1911","tid":656044,"uid":19213,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"都冇人鬧佢<br />\nBb豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90daf821a4072e8e951143c1d27ec3993b6ecaea","tid":656044,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c384b6a2983efa799bb443f73a6de12ec5a1911","tid":656044,"ui